<h4 class="c-media__title">
<a href="research/detox/" class="c-media__title-link">
Detox	</a>
</h4>
<p class="c-media__text">
During detoxification, the abused drugs or alcohol are flushed from the system in a measured fashion. This is a challenging but critical step due to the withdrawal symptoms.	</p>
<a href="research/detox/" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary">
Learn More
</a>
</div>
</div>
