<a href="research/rehab/" class="c-media__title-link">
Rehab	</a>
</h4>
<p class="c-media__text">
Once detox is completed, the rehabilitation phase starts. The body and mind now begin their recovery while therapy carves a path toward long-term success and patient health.	</p>
<a href="research/rehab/" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary">
Learn More
</a>
